main_body:
For the 2006/07 marketing year, the aid for tomatoes under Article 2 of Regulation (EC) No 2201/96 shall be:
(a) EUR 34,50 per tonne in the Czech Republic, Greece, France, Cyprus, Hungary, Malta, Poland, Portugal, and Slovakia;
(b) EUR 30,43 per tonne in Italy;
(c) in Spain:
(i) EUR 34,50 per tonne for tomatoes for processing into whole peeled tomatoes,
(ii) EUR 23,35 per tonne for tomatoes intended for other processing.
